# Ignore all
*
*/

# Except directories
!*/
!.gitignore

# Keep only essential folders
!Assets/
!Packages/
!ProjectSettings/

# Exclude generated/temporary files from included folders
Library/
Temp/
Logs/
UserSettings/
Builds/
Build/

# Visual Studio
*.csproj
*.sln
.vscode/
.vs/

# Generated files
*.userprefs
*.csproj.bak
*.meta

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
